This paper is about analyzing the welfare of auctions, which is a topic in game theory and mechanism design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory). The paper specifically focuses on first price auctions, which are a common type of auction in economics and computer science, so cs.EC (Economics and Computation) is also a likely category. The paper uses mathematical techniques to analyze the welfare of the auction, so cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also possible categories. Finally, the paper uses techniques from optimization and probability theory, which are common in machine learning and statistics, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely but still possible category.
